node.text:
I purchased my shirt from @simimoonlight a while back 🤎 | In the midst of everything that is going on right now and in support of the Black Lives Matter movement, I just wanted to come on the TL with a reminder of who we are and to encourage each of you to use YOUR gifts for the betterment of the Black community! 🖤 We were built for this! Our Ancestors manifested the strength that we are seeing around the world today. Leave me a comment letting me know what ways you are planning on impacting change for Black people locally, or globally for your chance to win a free manifestation journal. Respond to each other’s comments, drop resources, whatever you can! The time to manifest a better reality is NOW! ✨ DM me the word “giveaway” and I’ll ask for shipping info from the winners by Monday at 5pm est. Keep using your gifts for change. I love you! 🖤⁣
⁣
This post is 100% my own and the giveaway is not sponsored by anyone. NO BRANDED CONTENT. Just something I thought would be a creative way for us to share resources and ideas while also encouraging y’all to get into your manifestation bags! ⁣
⁣

node.text:
I’ve always known that I wanted to be a wife, but I never could’ve imagined the joy of being your wife… ⁣
⁣
Over the past year and a half, we’ve been through so many things together. ⁣
⁣
The way that you’ve taken care of me as a girlfriend leaves no doubt in my mind about the care that I’ll receive as your wife. ⁣
⁣
I am so happy and honored to have been given the opportunity to reciprocate and add to your love for the rest of our lives. ⁣
⁣
I’m so excited to embark on this new adventure with you. To find new ways to love you. To pursue my best on a daily basis with you.⁣
⁣
You have me for life, baby. Thank you for choosing me 🤍⁣ ⁣
⁣
📸: @whoelsebutgiles ⁣
